Q:1/4=76
K:Amix
H:Composed for Great Highland Pipe (chanter).
H:Range: G4 - A5. Scale: A mixolydian (9-note chanter, all notes used).
H:Form: AABA, 32 bars total. Slow march, q = 76.
H:Mood: dignified, drover walking cattle through highland mist.
H:NO RESTS — phrase ends are held tones, not silences. Doublings on
H:long notes; throw on D when D follows a lower pitch.
